wAg\">The Manual of Life - Character</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.upliftifyer.com/what_is_kindness.html\">What is Kindness?</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Kalchuri, Bhau (1986). <i>Meher Prabhu: Lord Meher</i>, <b>11</b>, Myrtle Beach: Manifestation, Inc., p. 3918.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Adam Phillips &amp; Barbara Taylor, <i>On Kindness</i> (London 2009) p. 12</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Phillips, p. 94</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.wavesofkindness.org\">Waves of Kindness</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Lagrette Tallent Lenker, <i>Fathers and Daughters in Shakespeare and Shaw</i> (2001) p. 107</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-14\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">robert Louis Stevenson, <i>Virginibus Puerisque</i> (London 1909) p. 35</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-15\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-15\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Galatians 5:22, New International Version</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Further_reading\">Further reading</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Kindness&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Further reading\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <span class=\"citation journal\">RABBI-UL-AWWAL (July 1998). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.islamicvoice.com/july.98/hadith.htm\">\"What is Kindness to Parents?\"</a>. <i>Islamic Voice</i>. 12-07 (139).</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKindness&amp;rft.atitle=What+is+Kindness+to+Parents%3F&amp;rft.aulast=RABBI-UL-AWWAL&amp;rft.au=RABBI-UL-AWWAL&amp;rft.date=July+1998&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.islamicvoice.com%2Fjuly.98%2Fhadith.htm&amp;rft.issue=139&amp;rft.jtitle=Islamic+Voice&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.volume=12-07\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li> <span class=\"citation web\">El-Sayed M. Amin. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20050828042644/http://www.islamonline.net/English/introducingislam/society/Neighborhoods/article02.shtml\">\"Kindness to a Non-Muslim Neighbor: Tips for Interaction\"</a>. <i>Society</i>. Islam Online. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.islamonline.net/English/introducingislam/society/Neighborhoods/article02.shtml\">the original</a> on 2005-08-28<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2005-11-22</span></span>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKindness&amp;rft.atitle=Kindness+to+a+Non-Muslim+Neighbor%3A+Tips+for+Interaction&amp;rft.au=El-Sayed+M.+Amin&amp;rft.aulast=El-Sayed+M.+Amin&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.islamonline.net%2FEnglish%2Fintroducingislam%2Fsociety%2FNeighborhoods%2Farticle02.shtml&amp;rft.jtitle=Society&amp;rft.pub=Islam+Online&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Kindness&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kindness.com.au\">Australian Kindness Movement</a></li></ul>\n"}]}}}, "warnings": {"query": {"*": "Formatting of continuation data will be changing soon. To continue using the current formatting, use the 'rawcontinue' parameter. To begin using the new format, pass an empty string for 'continue' in the initial query."}}}